These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-1::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: documentary, horror, satire, comedy
There are 4 different nationalities: chinese, egyptian, thai, turkish
1. the egyptian is on the left of the chinese##1
2. the person watching documentary movies is the turkish##1
3. the thai is on the right of the chinese##1
4. the person watching horror movies is on the left of the turkish##1
5. the person watching comedy movies is on the left of the chinese##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |   3    |    4    |
| Movie-Genre          | comedy | satire | horror | documentary   |
| Nationality   | egyptian  | chinese     | thai   | turkish |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-2::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: camping, cooking, video-games, woodworking
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: house, metal, blues, classical
1. the person who's hobby is woodworking is the fan of metal##1
2. the person who's hobby is camping is on the far right##1
3. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
4. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the right of the fan of blues##1
5. the fan of metal is on the left of the fan of house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |      2      |    3    |     4      |
| Hobby   | video-games | woodworking | cooking | camping    |
| Music-Genre   | blues    | metal      | house | classical |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-3::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: fishing, rock-climbing, traveling, writing
4 different games are played: domino, chess, billiard, backgammon
1. the person playing billiard is on the left of the person playing backgammon##1
2. the person who's hobby is fishing is the person playing domino##1
3. the person playing chess is on the far right##1
4. the person playing backgammon is on the right of the person who's hobby is writing##1
5. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the left of the person playing chess##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |      3      |       4       |
| Hobby         | fishing | writing | traveling   | rock-climbing |
| Game   | domino   | billiard | backgammon | chess         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-4::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: green, white, pink, black
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: basketball, sailing, surfing, tennis
1. the person who's sport is sailing is the person who likes black##1
2. the person who likes white is on the left of the person who's sport is surfing##1
3. the person who likes white is on the left of the person who likes green##1
4. the person who likes white is on the right of the person who likes black##1
5. the person who's sport is basketball is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Color   | black | white | green  | pink      |
| Sport         | sailing | tennis   | surfing | basketball |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-5::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: siglo, swisher, bolivar, vegafina
4 different pets are kept: dog, hamster, hedgehog, pony
1. the swisher-smoker is on the left of the siglo-smoker##1
2. the owner of the hedgehog is on the right of the bolivar-smoker##1
3. the vegafina-smoker is on the left of the owner of the pony##1
4. the owner of the hamster is on the right of the owner of the hedgehog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |  2   |    3     |      4      |
| Cigar   | vegafina | bolivar | swisher | siglo |
| Pet    | dog       | pony | hedgehog | hamster     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-6::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: electronic, hip-hop, salsa, ambient
4 different pets are kept: fish, frog, goldfish, mouse
1. the fan of hip-hop is on the far right##1
2. the fan of ambient is on the left of the fan of salsa##1
3. the owner of the mouse is on the left of the owner of the frog##1
4. the owner of the fish is on the left of the fan of salsa##1
5. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the owner of the goldfish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |   3   |    4    |
| Music-Genre   | ambient | salsa | electronic | hip-hop |
| Pet           | fish      | goldfish | mouse | frog    |

