.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-8::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  chef, designer, entrepreneur, musician
4 different pets are kept: rabbit, hamster, cat, goldfish
1. the owner of the goldfish is on the right of the designer##1
2. the owner of the goldfish is the musician##1
3. the designer is on the right of the chef##1
4. the entrepreneur is on the left of the owner of the hamster##1
5. the owner of the rabbit is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |     2     |    3     |    4     |
| Job         | entrepreneur | chef      | designer | musician |
| Pet   | rabbit          | hamster | cat     | goldfish    |

