.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-9::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: family, fantasy, spy, zombie
4 different games are played: bridge, billiard, go, backgammon
1. the person playing backgammon is on the left of the person playing bridge##1
2. the person watching family movies is on the left of the person playing bridge##1
3. the person watching zombie movies is on the far right##1
4. the person playing billiard is on the left of the person playing go##1
5. the person playing backgammon is on the right of the person watching spy movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |   3    |    4     |
| Movie-Genre   | fantasy    | spy       | family | zombie   |
| Game     | billiard | go | backgammon   | bridge |

