.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-11::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, milk, sprite, water
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: basketball, ice-hockey, sailing, volleyball
1. the person who's sport is sailing is on the right of the person who's sport is basketball##1
2. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the right of the person who's sport is sailing##1
3. the person drinking water is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
4. the person drinking sprite is on the far left##1
5. the person drinking milk is the person who's sport is sailing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |       3       |   4   |
| Beverage      | sprite | milk  | hot-chocolate | water |
| Sport   | basketball  | sailing | volleyball           | ice-hockey   |

