.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-12::.
There are 4 different nationalities: argentine, canadian, dutch, thai
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: august, december, october, january
1. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left of the argentine##1
2. the dutch is on the right of the thai##1
3. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left of the person who's birthday is in august##1
4. the argentine is on the right of the canadian##1
5. the person who's birthday is in october is on the right of the argentine##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |  3   |   4    |
| Nationality   | canadian | argentine | thai | dutch  |
| Birthday           | january | december      | october | august |

