.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-13::.
City: berlin, new-york, london, liverpool
4 different pets are kept: hamster, lizard, rabbit, rat
1. the owner of the rat is the person traveling to berlin##1
2. the owner of the lizard is on the left of the person traveling to berlin##1
3. the person traveling to london is the owner of the rabbit##1
4. the person traveling to london is on the left of the owner of the lizard##1
5. the person traveling to liverpool is on the right of the person traveling to berlin##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |   2    |   3    |    4    |
| City   | london | new-york  | berlin | liverpool   |
| Pet        | rabbit | lizard | rat    | hamster |

