.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-15::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: azalea, begonia, daisy, bellflower
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: parkour, skateboarding, soccer, swimming
1. the person who's sport is swimming is on the left of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
2. the person who's sport is swimming is on the far left##1
3. the person who growsbegonia is on the right of the person who's sport is parkour##1
4. the person who's sport is swimming is on the left of the person who growsbellflower##1
5. the person who's sport is soccer is on the right of the person who growsazalea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |       2       |     3     |    4     |
| Flower   | daisy | bellflower     | azalea | begonia |
| Sport         | swimming | skateboarding | parkour   | soccer   |

