3. the person watching horror movies is on the left of the person who growsamaryllis##1
4. the person watching comedy movies is on the right of the person watching western movies##1
5. the person who growstulip is on the right of the person who growsdaisy##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |   2    |    3    |   4    |
