.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-18::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, cola, fanta, soy-milk
The people use 4 different means of transport: boat, airplane, quad-bike, skateboard
1. the person drinking coffee is on the far left##1
2. the person driving the boat is on the far left##1
3. the person driving the airplane is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1
4. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person driving the skateboard##1
5. the person drinking cola is on the right of the person driving the skateboard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |   3    |     4      |
| Beverage      | coffee   | soy-milk | cola   | fanta      |
| Transport   | boat | skateboard      | airplane | quad-bike |

