.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-19::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: cooking, puzzles, rock-climbing, video-games
There 4 different types of food: corn, spinach, kale, garlic
1. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
2. the person eating garlic is on the left of the person eating kale##1
3. the person eating kale is the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
4. the person eating kale is on the left of the person eating corn##1
5. the person eating corn is on the left of the person who's hobby is cooking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |      3      |    4    |
| Hobby         | puzzles | rock-climbing | video-games | cooking |
| Food   | garlic     | kale    | corn      | spinach   |

